data.description: Come take a look at this beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath plus bonus room perfect for an office space or playroom with an amazing back yard, including a new large pool, spa, and water cooling system for hot summers. This great backyard also features an amazing outdoor kitchen with a firepit perfect for entertaining. The laundry room has ample cabinet space and a soaking sink. This property has two new AC units that help with the already low utilities in the city of Indio. The Property is close to schools, shopping, restaurants, and the 10 Fwy. A perfect location for an already growing city and upcoming developments, for example, Texas Road House and Movie Theater coming soon.
